    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="LeetCode个人题解¥"><a href="#LeetCode个人题解¥" class="headerlink" title="LeetCode个人题解¥"></a>LeetCode个人题解¥</h1><h3 id="11-盛最多水的容器"><a href="#11-盛最多水的容器" class="headerlink" title="[11]盛最多水的容器"></a>[11]盛最多水的容器</h3><p>这道中等题也不是特别难，我第一眼想到的是通过暴力输出找出最大的Area，但是O(n^2)固然不能这么做，我又想到如果我从两边向中间遍历，这样的话可以省去一半的重复遍历，因此就想到了之前刚用过的双指针，双指针的时间复杂度是O(n)。</p><figure class="highlight swift"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">func</span> <span class="title">maxArea</span><span class="params">(<span class="number">_</span> height: [Int])</span></span> -&gt; <span class="type">Int</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">var</span> <span class="keyword">left</span> = <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">var</span> <span class="keyword">right</span> = height.<span class="built_in">count</span> - <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">var</span> area = <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span> <span class="keyword">left</span> &lt; <span class="keyword">right</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            area = <span class="built_in">max</span>(area, <span class="built_in">min</span>(height[<span class="keyword">left</span>], height[<span class="keyword">right</span>]) * (<span class="keyword">right</span> - <span class="keyword">left</span>))</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> height[<span class="keyword">left</span>] &lt; height[<span class="keyword">right</span>] &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">left</span> += <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">            &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> height[<span class="keyword">left</span>] &gt; height[<span class="keyword">right</span>] &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">right</span> -= <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">            &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">left</span> += <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">right</span> -= <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> area</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>简单说一下，主要的思路就是从两端设置指针向中间移动，由于移动指针指向的两个“桶边”中较高的一边的话，Area的面积必定会减小，因此我们用到了类似博弈的想法，既然小的那边已经很小了，那么我们移动一下，万一下一个是更大的呢？如果两个都是同样高度的话，就同时移动。</p><h3 id="14-最长公共前缀"><a href="#14-最长公共前缀" class="headerlink" title="[14]最长公共前缀"></a>[14]最长公共前缀</h3><p>这道题挺简单的，就用到了有关字符串的操作，直接秒了。学到了一个可以直接检查字符串开头是否与给定的字符串相同</p><figure class="highlight swift"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">let</span> apple = <span class="string">&quot;ILoveApple&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(apple.hasPrefix(<span class="string">&quot;iLove&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//Prints &quot;false&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>同理还有检查结尾是否相同的</p><figure class="highlight swift"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(apple.hasSuffix(<span class="string">&quot;ple&quot;</span>))</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//Prints &quot;true&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="15-三数之和"><a href="#15-三数之和" class="headerlink" title="[15]三数之和"></a>[15]三数之和</h3><p>leetCode里写的第一道中等题，太魔鬼了…第一次手写的究极遍历大法三次循环直接干到O(n^3)，然后华丽地超时了。</p><p>看了大佬的题解之后：</p><figure class="highlight swift"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">func</span> <span class="title">threeSum</span><span class="params">(<span class="number">_</span> nums: [Int])</span></span> -&gt; [[<span class="type">Int</span>]] &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> nums.<span class="built_in">count</span> &lt;= <span class="number">2</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> []</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//<span class="doctag">TODO:</span> sort()与sorted()的区别</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">let</span> nums = nums.sorted()</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">var</span> result = [[<span class="type">Int</span>]]()</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> nums[<span class="number">0</span>] &gt; <span class="number">0</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> []</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> index <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="number">0</span> ..&lt; nums.<span class="built_in">count</span> - <span class="number">1</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> index &gt; <span class="number">0</span> &amp;&amp; nums[index - <span class="number">1</span>] == nums[index] &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">continue</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">var</span> lowPoint = index + <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">var</span> heighPoint = nums.<span class="built_in">count</span> - <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">let</span> targetNum = <span class="number">0</span> - nums[index]</span><br><span class="line">        </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span> lowPoint &lt; heighPoint &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">let</span> sum = nums[lowPoint] + nums[heighPoint]</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> targetNum == sum &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                result.append([nums[index], nums[lowPoint], nums[heighPoint]])</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">while</span> (lowPoint &lt; heighPoint &amp;&amp; nums[lowPoint] == nums[lowPoint + <span class="number">1</span>]) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                lowPoint += <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">while</span> (lowPoint &lt; heighPoint &amp;&amp; nums[heighPoint] == nums[heighPoint - <span class="number">1</span>]) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                heighPoint -= <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            lowPoint += <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">            heighPoint -= <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">            &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> sum &gt; targetNum &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                heighPoint -= <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">            &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                lowPoint += <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> result</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>实现的方法还是蛮简单的，算是二数之和的一个变种，</p><p>我首先对数组进行排序，让数字排列有规律，更利于去寻找答案。</p><p>其次外层循环确定一个主数字i，然后通过双指针lowPoint和heighPoint同时去遍历数组，找到使</p><figure class="highlight swift"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nums[lowPoint] + nums[heighPoint] = <span class="number">0</span> - nums[i]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>成立的一个数组，就将其加入到result二维数组内。此时此刻我要去进行检查，查看lowPoint指针的后一个数字是否和当前lowPoint对应的数字相同，如果相同便一直循环+1直到</p><figure class="highlight swift"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nums[lowPoint + <span class="number">1</span>] != nums[lowPoint]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>同理heighPoint要对其前面的数字进行检查，循环-1。双while循环运行完毕之后，此时lowPoint和heighPoint都位于重复数字的边缘，再运行</p><figure class="highlight swift"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">lowPoint += <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">heighPoint -= <span class="number">1</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>让指针移动到新的数字上。（过滤重复）</p><p>之后就是三个if，因为我们之前已经从小到大给数列排序了，如果当前sum总和大于我们要的targetNum，那我们就将heighPoint左移一位，这样可以使我们当前的sum总和变小，反之将lowPoint右移可以使整个sum总和变大（太妙了这个方法</p><p>最后return出结果就好了。</p><h3 id="20-有效的括号"><a href="#20-有效的括号" class="headerlink" title="[20]有效的括号"></a>[20]有效的括号</h3><p>很有意思的一道简单题，学习了数组栈的实现方法，顺便试了试正则表达式。</p><figure class="highlight swift"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Solution</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//40:( 41:( 91:[ 93:] 123:&#123; 125:&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">func</span> <span class="title">isValid</span><span class="params">(<span class="number">_</span> s: String)</span></span> -&gt; <span class="type">Bool</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">let</span> brackets = <span class="type">Array</span>(s)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">var</span> stack = [<span class="type">Character</span>]()</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> index <span class="keyword">in</span> brackets &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">switch</span> index &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&quot;(&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;[&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;&#123;&quot;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                stack.append(index)</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&quot;)&quot;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">if</span> stack.popLast() != <span class="string">&quot;(&quot;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&quot;]&quot;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">if</span> stack.popLast() != <span class="string">&quot;[&quot;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&quot;&#125;&quot;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">if</span> stack.popLast() != <span class="string">&quot;&#123;&quot;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">default</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> stack.isEmpty &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>首先我们来分析这道题，括号如果想要有效匹配，就需要找到他的另一对，而且有效括号的嵌套关系是固定的，不会出现括号穿插的情况，因此我们可以通过声明一个数组栈只用来存储从左到右遍历到的左括号，当遇到第一个右括号时，通过popLast()方法弹出最后一个进栈的左括号与其进行配对，如果是相同类型的括号，则抵消掉，反之则直接输出false即可。直到外层循环结束，若栈内无多余的左括号，则说明所有括号都匹配成功抵消掉了，因此返回true，反之返回false。</p><h3 id="21-合并两个有序链表"><a href="#21-合并两个有序链表" class="headerlink" title="[21]合并两个有序链表"></a>[21]合并两个有序链表</h3><figure class="highlight swift"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">func</span> <span class="title">mergeTwoLists</span><span class="params">(<span class="number">_</span> l1: ListNode?, <span class="number">_</span> l2: ListNode?)</span></span> -&gt; <span class="type">ListNode?</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">var</span> firstNode = l1</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">var</span> secondNode = l2</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">var</span> prep = <span class="type">ListNode</span>(-<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">var</span> head: <span class="type">ListNode?</span> = prep</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> firstNode?.val != <span class="literal">nil</span> &amp;&amp; secondNode?.val != <span class="literal">nil</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> firstNode?.val ?? <span class="number">0</span> &lt;= secondNode?.val ?? <span class="number">0</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            head?.next = firstNode</span><br><span class="line">            firstNode = firstNode?.next</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            head?.next = secondNode</span><br><span class="line">            secondNode = secondNode?.next</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        head = head?.next</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    head?.next = firstNode ?? secondNode</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> prep.next</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>之前对链表一直不是特别熟悉，今天尝试着用了一下。</p><p>这道题解法的主要核心就是哨兵节点，首先声明一个节点prep用于最后返回数据使用。其次我们为了方便操作，再次新建一个head节点，将其prep传入head节点。其次的逻辑非常简单，只需判断l1和l2当前节点的大小，谁小就将其与head.next链接，此时要注意一共三步操作：1、将较小值与head.next链接，2、head = head.next，3、原链表指针后移。 </p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
